#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Help System Handbook"
msgstr "&kde; priročnik sistema pomoči"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help System"
msgstr "Sistem pomoči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The help system is designed to make accessing the common &UNIX; help systems "
"(<application>man</application> and <application>info</application>) simple, "
"as well as the user documentation of applications including &plasma-"
"workspaces; from the &kde; community (&XML;)."
msgstr ""
"The help system is designed to make accessing the common &UNIX; help systems "
"(<application>man</application> and <application>info</application>) simple, "
"as well as the user documentation of applications including &plasma-"
"workspaces; from the &kde; community (&XML;).The help system is designed to "
"make accessing the common &UNIX; help systems (<application>man</"
"application> and <application>info</application>) simple, as well as the "
"user documentation of applications including &plasma-workspaces; from the "
"&kde; community (&XML;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All applications (including &plasma-workspaces;) from the &kde; community "
"come fully documented, thanks to the efforts of the Documentation team. If "
"you are interested in helping with the documentation efforts, join the "
"<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-doc-english\">mailing "
"list</ulink> and write to the team at <email>kde-doc-english@kde.org</"
"email>. No experience is required, just enthusiasm and patience."
msgstr ""
"Vse aplikacije (vključno z &plasma-workspaces;) iz skupnosti &kde; so po "
"zaslugi prizadevanj ekipe za dokumentacijo v celoti dokumentirane. Če želite "
"pomagati pri dokumentiranju, se pridružite <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/"
"mailman/listinfo/kde-doc-english\">poštnemu seznamu</ulink> in pišite ekipi "
"na <email>kde-doc-english@kde.org</email>. Izkušnje niso potrebne, le "
"navdušenje in potrpežljivost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you would like to help translating &kde; documentation to your native "
"language, review the information, including coordinators for each language "
"team, on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">Localization web site</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pomagati pri prevajanju dokumentacije &kde; v svoj materni jezik, "
"si oglejte informacije, vključno s koordinatorji za vsako jezikovno skupino, "
"na <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">Lokalizacijsko spletno mesto</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invoking Help"
msgstr "Priklic pomoči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "&khelpcenter; can be called in several ways:"
msgstr "&khelpcenter; lahko prikličete na več načinov:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu"
msgstr "V meniju <guimenu>Help</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common will probably be from within an application. Choose "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Help</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Application</replaceable> Handbook</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to open that application's handbook."
msgstr ""
"Najpogostejša možnost je verjetno iz aplikacije. Izberite <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem><replaceable>Aplikacije</"
"replaceable> Priročnik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in odprite priročnik te "
"aplikacije."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the Application Launcher"
msgstr "Iz zaganjalnika aplikacij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the big <guiicon>K</guiicon> in your panel, and select "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem> from the <guimenuitem>Applications</"
"guimenuitem> tab or type <userinput>help</userinput> followed by selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem>. This will open &khelpcenter; with the "
"default start page."
msgstr ""
"Na plošči izberite velik <guiicon>K</guiicon> in na zavihku "
"<guimenuitem>Aplikacije</guimenuitem> izberite <guimenuitem>Pomoč</"
"guimenuitem> ali vnesite <userinput>pomoč</userinput> in nato izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Pomoč</guimenuitem>. To bo odprlo program &khelpcenter; s "
"privzeto začetno stranjo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the command line"
msgstr "Iz ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; may be started using a &URL; to display a file. &URL;s have "
"been added for <command>info</command> and <command>man</command> pages "
"also. You can use them as follows:"
msgstr ""
"&khelpcenter; se lahko zažene z uporabo &URL; za prikaz datoteke. &URL;i so "
"bili dodani tudi za strani <command>info</command> in <command>man</"
"command>. Uporabite jih lahko na naslednji način:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "An application help file"
msgstr "Datoteka pomoči neke aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the &kwrite; help file, at the contents page."
msgstr "Odpre datoteko pomoči &kwrite; na strani z vsebino."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "A local &URL;"
msgstr "Lokalni &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Man page"
msgstr "Man stran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "An Info page"
msgstr "Info stran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invoking <command>khelpcenter</command> with no parameters opens the default "
"start page."
msgstr ""
"Priklic <command>khelpcenter</command> brez parametrov odpre privzeto "
"začetno stran."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface"
msgstr "&khelpcenter; vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface consists of two panes of information."
msgstr "Vmesnik &khelpcenter; je sestavljen iz dveh oken z informacijami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar and menus are explained further in <xref linkend=\"menu-and-"
"toolbar-ref\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica in meniji so podrobneje razloženi v <xref linkend=\"menu-and-"
"toolbar-ref\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Documents contain their own navigation tools, enabling you to move either "
"sequentially through a document, using <guilabel>Next</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Previous</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> links, or "
"to move around in a less structured manner, using hyperlinks."
msgstr ""
"Dokumenti vsebujejo lastna navigacijska orodja, ki vam omogočajo zaporedno "
"premikanje po dokumentu s povezavami <guilabel>Naslednji</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Prejšnji</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vsebine</guilabel> ali manj "
"strukturirano premikanje s hiperpovezavami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Links can take you to other parts of the same document, or to a different "
"document, and you can use the <guiicon>Back</guiicon> (Left pointing arrow) "
"or <guiicon>Forward</guiicon> (Right pointing arrow) icons on the toolbar to "
"move through the documents you have viewed in this session."
msgstr ""
"Povezave vas lahko vodijo do drugih delov istega dokumenta ali do drugega "
"dokumenta, za premikanje po dokumentih, ki ste si jih ogledali v tej seji, "
"pa lahko uporabite ikoni <guiicon>Back</guiicon> (puščica v levo) ali "
"<guiicon>Forward</guiicon> (puščica v desno) v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The two panes display the contents of the help system, and the help files "
"themselves, on the left and right respectively."
msgstr ""
"V obeh podoknih je na levi strani prikazana vsebina sistema pomoči, na desni "
"pa same datoteke pomoči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Pane"
msgstr "Podokno z vsebino"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane in &khelpcenter; is displayed on the left hand side of the "
"window. As you might expect, you can move the splitter bar, to make sure you "
"can comfortably read the contents of either pane."
msgstr ""
"Podokno z vsebino v programu &khelpcenter; je prikazano na levi strani okna. "
"Ko lahko pričakujete, lahko premikate razdelilno vrstico, da lahko udobno "
"preberete vsebino obeh podoken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane is further divided into three tabs, one containing a <link "
"linkend=\"contents-tab\">tree view</link> showing all the help information "
"&khelpcenter; is aware of, and the other contains the &kde; <link linkend="
"\"kde-glossary\">glossary</link> of terms. On the third tab you can "
"configure the <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Podokno z vsebino je nadalje razdeljeno na tri zavihke, od katerih prvi "
"vsebuje <link linkend=\"contents-tab\">drevesni prikaz</link>, v katerem so "
"prikazane vse informacije pomoči, ki jih &khelpcenter; pozna, drugi pa "
"vsebuje<link linkend=\"kde-glossary\">slovar</link> izrazov &kde;. V tretjem "
"zavihku lahko konfigurirate <guilabel>Možnosti iskanja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek z vsebino"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> tab contains the following default top "
"level entries in the tree view:"
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Vsebine</guilabel> vsebuje naslednje privzete vnose "
"najvišjih ravni v drevesnem prikazu:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fundamentals"
msgstr "Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Fundamentals introduce you to the many features of the &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications; and describe many common tasks you can "
"perform in all &applications;."
msgstr ""
"Osnove vas seznanijo s številnimi funkcijami &plasma-workspaces; in "
"&applications; ter opisujejo številna običajna opravila, ki jih lahko "
"izvajate v vseh &applications;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma Manual"
msgstr "Priročnik Plasma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &plasma; Manual is the documentation for the &plasma-workspaces;."
msgstr "Priročnik &plasma; je dokumentacija za &plasma-workspaces;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "Pomoč na spletu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A page with links to online help and additional information provided by the "
"&kde; community."
msgstr ""
"Stran s povezavami do spletne pomoči in dodatnih informacij, ki jih "
"zagotavlja skupnost &kde;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Manuals"
msgstr "Priročniki za aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Native &kde; application documentation. All &kde; applications have "
"documentation in &XML; format, which are converted to <acronym>HTML</"
"acronym> when you view them. This section lists all the &kde; applications "
"with a brief description and a link to the full application documentation."
msgstr ""
"Nativna dokumentacija za aplikacije. Vsi programi &kde; imajo dokumentacijo "
"v obliki &XML;, ki se ob ogledu pretvori v <acronym>HTML</acronym>. V tem "
"razdelku so navedene vse aplikacije &kde; s kratkim opisom in povezavo do "
"celotne dokumentacije aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The applications are displayed in a tree structure that echoes the default "
"structure of the <guimenu>K</guimenu> menu, making it easy to find the "
"application you are looking for."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacije so prikazane v drevesni strukturi, ki je enaka privzeti strukturi "
"menija <guimenu>K</guimenu>, tako da zlahka najdete želeno aplikacijo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Settings Modules</guilabel> entities"
msgstr "<guilabel>Moduli nastavitev</guilabel> entitete"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provide a list of links to various modules in the &systemsettings; "
"application or to modules for &konqueror;, Filemanager or Browser."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovijo seznam povezav do različnih modulov v aplikaciji &systemsettings; "
"ali do modulov za &konqueror;, Filemanager ali Browser."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "KInfoCenter Modules"
msgstr "KInfoCenter moduli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contains a list of links to various KInfocenter modules documentation."
msgstr "Vsebuje seznam povezav do dokumentacije različnih modulov KInfocentra."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "KIO Workers"
msgstr "KIO Workers"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contains a list of links to various <acronym>KIO</acronym> modules "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Vsebuje seznam povezav do dokumentacije različnih modulov <acronym>KIO</"
"acronym>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "&UNIX; manual pages"
msgstr "Strani &UNIX; priročnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&UNIX; man pages are the traditional on-line documentation format for &UNIX; "
"systems. Most programs on your system will have a man page. In addition, man "
"pages exist for programming functions and file formats."
msgstr ""
"&UNIX; man strani so tradicionalna oblika spletne dokumentacije za sisteme "
"&UNIX;. Večina programov v vašem sistemu ima stran z navodili za uporabo. "
"Poleg tega so na voljo tudi priročniške strani za programske funkcije in "
"datotečne formate."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrollkeeper"
msgstr "Scrollkeeper"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional non-&kde; documentation installed on your system."
msgstr "Dodatna dokumentacija, ki ni&kde; nameščena v vašem sistemu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse Info Pages"
msgstr "Brskanje po informativnih straneh"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"TeXinfo documentation is used by many &GNU; applications, including "
"<command>gcc</command> (the C/C++ compiler), <command>emacs</command>, and "
"many others."
msgstr ""
"Dokumentacijo TeXinfo uporabljajo številni &GNU; programi, vključno z "
"<command>gcc</command> (prevajalnik C/C++), <command>emacs</command> in "
"številni drugi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Zavihek <guilabel>Možnosti iskanja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching the help files is fairly intuitive, enter the word(s) you wish to "
"search for in the text box, choose your options (if any), and press "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton>. The results display in the viewer pane to the "
"right."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje po datotekah pomoči je dokaj intuitivno, v besedilno polje vnesite "
"besedo(-e), ki jo(-e) želite poiskati, izberite možnosti (če obstajajo) in "
"pritisnite <guibutton>Poišči</guibutton>. Rezultati so prikazani v podoknu "
"pregledovalnika na desni strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search is not case sensitive, &ie; uppercase and lowercase characters are "
"considered the same. For example, if you search for <quote>Shortcut</quote>, "
"results that contain <quote>shortcut</quote> will be returned as well."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje ne upošteva velikih in malih črk, zato se velike in male črke "
"štejejo za enake. Če na primer iščete <quote>Bližnjice</quote>, bodo vrnjeni "
"tudi rezultati, ki vsebujejo <quote>bližnjice</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "The options available are:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Method"
msgstr "Metoda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose how to search for multiple words. If you choose <guilabel>and</"
"guilabel>, results are returned only if all your search terms are included "
"in the page. <guilabel>or</guilabel> returns results if <emphasis>any</"
"emphasis> of the search terms are found."
msgstr ""
"Izberite način iskanja več besed. Če izberete <guilabel>in</guilabel>, se "
"rezultati vrnejo le, če so na strani vključeni vsi iskalni izrazi. "
"<guilabel>ali</guilabel> vrne rezultate, če so najdeni <emphasis>kateri "
"koli</emphasis> iskalni izrazi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your searches are not returning the results you expect, check carefully "
"you haven't excluded the wrong search term with an erroneous setting."
msgstr ""
"Če iskanja ne prinašajo pričakovanih rezultatov, skrbno preverite, ali niste "
"z napačno nastavitvijo izključili prave iskalne besede."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max. results"
msgstr "Maksimalni rezultati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Determines the maximum number of results returned from your search."
msgstr "Določa največje število vrnjenih rezultatov iskanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scope selection"
msgstr "Izbira področja uporabe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to select the sections where the search will be done. The "
"available options quickly select the most common option, while "
"<guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem> allows one to select single sections."
msgstr ""
"S tem se izberejo razdelki, v katerih se bo izvajalo iskanje. Z "
"razpoložljivimi možnostmi hitro izberete najpogostejšo možnost, "
"<guimenuitem>Po meri</guimenuitem> pa omogoča izbiro posameznih razdelkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>Man</application> and <application>Info</application> "
"sections"
msgstr ""
"Razdelka <application>Man</application> in <application>Info</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man pages are the standard &UNIX; manual pages, and have been in use for "
"many years on many operating systems. They are extremely thorough, and are "
"the very best place to get information about most &UNIX; commands and "
"applications. When people say <quote>RTFM</quote>, the Manual they are "
"referring to is very often the man page."
msgstr ""
"Priročniške strani so standardne priročniške strani &UNIX; in se že vrsto "
"let uporabljajo v številnih operacijskih sistemih. So izredno temeljite in "
"tako najboljše mesto za pridobivanje informacij o večini ukazov &UNIX; in "
"aplikacij. Ko ljudje rečejo <quote>RTFM</quote> (Read the f*cking manual - "
"preberite j*bena navodila, pogost akronim na internetu), je priročnik, na "
"katerega se sklicujejo, zelo pogosto stran man."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The man pages are not perfect. They tend to be in depth, but also extremely "
"technical, often written by developers, and for developers. In some cases "
"this makes them somewhat unfriendly, if not downright impossible for many "
"users to understand. They are, however, the best source of solid information "
"on most command line applications, and very often the only source."
msgstr ""
"Strani man niso popolne. Navadno so poglobljene, a tudi zelo tehnične, "
"pogosto jih pišejo razvijalci za razvijalce. V nekaterih primerih so zaradi "
"tega za mnoge uporabnike nekoliko neprijazne ali celo povsem nerazumljive. "
"Kljub temu so najboljši vir zanesljivih informacij o večini aplikacij ukazne "
"vrstice in zelo pogosto tudi edini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you've ever wondered what the number is when people write things like "
"man(1) it means which section of the manual the item is in. You will see "
"&khelpcenter; uses the numbers to divide the very many man pages into their "
"own sections, making it easier for you to find the information you're "
"looking for, if you're just browsing."
msgstr ""
"Če ste se kdaj spraševali, kaj je številka, ko ljudje pišejo npr. man(1), to "
"pomeni, v katerem delu priročnika je ta element. Videli boste, da "
"&khelpcenter; uporablja številke za razdelitev velike količine priročniških "
"strani v lastne razdelke, kar vam olajša iskanje informacij, ki jih iščete, "
"če samo brskate skozi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also available are the Info pages, intended to be a replacement for the man "
"pages. The maintainer of some applications no longer update the man pages, "
"so if there is both a man page and an info page available, the info page is "
"probably the most recent. Most applications have one or the other though. If "
"the application you are looking for help on is a &GNU; utility, you will "
"most likely find it has an info page, not a man page."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so tudi informativne strani, ki naj bi nadomestile strani man. "
"Vzdrževalci nekaterih aplikacij ne posodabljajo več strani priročnika, zato "
"je, če sta na voljo tako stran priročnika kot informacijska stran, verjetno "
"najnovejša informacijska stran. Večina aplikacij ima eno ali drugo. Če je "
"aplikacija, za katero iščete pomoč, pripomoček &GNU;, boste najverjetneje "
"našli informacijsko stran in ne strani man."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating inside the <application>Info</application> pages"
msgstr "Navigacija znotraj strani <application>Info</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info documents are arranged hierarchically with each page called a node. All "
"info documents have a <guilabel>Top</guilabel> node, &ie; the opening page. "
"You can return to the <guilabel>Top</guilabel> of an info document by "
"pressing <guilabel>Top</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Informacijski dokumenti so urejeni hierarhično, vsaka stran se imenuje "
"vozlišče. Vsi informativni dokumenti imajo vozlišče <guilabel>Vrh</"
"guilabel>, &ie; uvodno stran. Na <guilabel>Vrh</guilabel> informacijskega "
"dokumenta se lahko vrnete tako, da pritisnete <guilabel>Vrh</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Prev</guibutton> &amp; <guibutton>Next</guibutton> are used to "
"move to the previous/next page at the current level of the hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Prev</guibutton> &amp; <guibutton>Next</guibutton> se uporabljata "
"za prehod na prejšnjo/naslednjo stran na trenutni ravni hierarhije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a menu item within a document moves you to a lower level in the "
"hierarchy. You may move up the hierarchy by pressing <guibutton>Up</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na element menija v dokumentu se premaknete na nižjo raven v "
"hierarhiji. Hierarhijo lahko nadgradite s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Gor</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man is treated similarly to info, with the section index being the Top node "
"and each man page on the level below. Man entries are one page long."
msgstr ""
"Man je obravnavan podobno kot info, pri čemer je kazalo razdelka zgornje "
"vozlišče, vsaka stran man pa je na nižji ravni. Prispevki man so dolgi eno "
"stran."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kde; glossary"
msgstr "Ekipa &kde; glosar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The glossary provides a quick reference point, where you can look up the "
"definitions of words that may be unfamiliar to you. These range from &kde; "
"specific applications and technologies, through to general &UNIX; computing "
"terms."
msgstr ""
"Slovar je hitra referenčna točka, v kateri lahko poiščete definicije besed, "
"ki vam morda niso znane. Te segajo od posebnih aplikacij in tehnologij do "
"splošnih računalniških izrazov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the left hand pane you will see a tree view, with two choices: "
"<guilabel>Alphabetically</guilabel> or <guilabel>By Topic</guilabel>. Both "
"contain the same entries, sorted differently, to allow you to quickly find "
"the item of interest."
msgstr ""
"V levem podoknu je prikazan drevesni prikaz z dvema možnostma: <guilabel>Po "
"abecedi</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Po temah</guilabel>. Oba vsebujeta enake "
"vnose, ki so različno razvrščeni, da lahko hitro poiščete želeni element."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate down the tree views to the left, and items you select will be "
"displayed on the right."
msgstr ""
"Po drevesnih prikazih se pomikate navzdol po levi strani, izbrani elementi "
"pa se prikažejo na desni strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus and toolbar"
msgstr "Meniji in orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; has a very minimal interface, allowing you to concentrate on "
"getting help rather than learning how to use the help browser."
msgstr ""
"&khelpcenter; ima zelo minimalen uporabniški vmesnik, zato se lahko "
"osredotočite na pridobivanje pomoči in ne na učenje uporabe brskalnika za "
"pomoč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "The icons available to you in the toolbar are as follows:"
msgstr "V orodni vrstici so na voljo naslednje ikone:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar Icons"
msgstr "Ikone orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "Kazalo vsebine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490 index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the main start page of &khelpcenter;."
msgstr "Pojdite na glavno začetno stran &khelpcenter;."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Back"
msgstr "Nazaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the previous page you viewed. Click the check mark right to the icon. "
"This displays a list of previously viewed pages. Selecting one will take you "
"directly back to that page."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na prejšnjo stran, ki ste si jo ogledali. Kliknite kljukico desno od "
"ikone. Prikaže se seznam predhodno ogledanih strani. Če izberete eno od "
"njih, se vrnete neposredno na to stran."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward"
msgstr "Naprej"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go forward one page. This icon is only active if you have already used the "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite eno stran naprej. Ta ikona je aktivna le, če ste že uporabili ikono "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopiraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy text to the clipboard to be pasted in another application."
msgstr "Kopirajte besedilo v odložišče in ga vstavite v drugo aplikacijo."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Poišči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find a word or words within the currently visible page."
msgstr "Poiščite besedo ali besede na trenutno vidni strani."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase Font Sizes"
msgstr "Povečaj velikost pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase the size of the text in the viewer pane."
msgstr "Povečajte velikost besedila v podoknu pregledovalnika."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decrease Font Sizes"
msgstr "Zmanjšaj velikost pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decrease the size of the text in the viewer pane. This icon is only enabled "
"if you have previously enlarged the text."
msgstr ""
"Zmanjšajte velikost besedila v podoknu pregledovalnika. Ta ikona je "
"omogočena le, če ste besedilo predhodno povečali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus contain the following entries:"
msgstr "V menijih so naslednji vnosi:"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "File"
msgstr "Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Print the contents of the currently visible page. Handbooks in <acronym>PDF</"
"acronym> format you find on the <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/index.php?"
"language=en\"> &kde; Documentation Server</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Natisne vsebino trenutno vidne strani. Priročnike v formatu <acronym>PDF</"
"acronym> najdete na <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/index.php?language=en"
"\"> &kde; Documentacijski strežnik</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close and exit &khelpcenter;"
msgstr "Zapri in zapusti &khelpcenter;"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Uredi"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy the selected text to the clipboard."
msgstr "Kopirajte izbrano besedilo v odložišče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select all the text in the current page."
msgstr "Izberite vse besedilo na trenutni strani."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find a word or words in the currently visible page."
msgstr "Poiščite besedo ali besede na trenutno vidni strani."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Set Encoding</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Nastavi kodiranje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the encoding of the current page. Normally, the default setting of "
"<guimenuitem>Default</guimenuitem> should be sufficient, but if you are "
"having problems viewing pages written in languages other than English, you "
"may need to choose a specific encoding in this menu."
msgstr ""
"Spremeni kodiranje trenutne strani. Običajno zadostuje privzeta nastavitev "
"<guimenuitem>Privzeto</guimenuitem>, če pa imate težave z ogledom strani, "
"napisanih v drugih jezikih, boste morda morali v tem meniju izbrati določeno "
"kodiranje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Full Screen Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Celozaslonski način</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes &khelpcenter; to full screen mode, in which the &khelpcenter; window "
"takes up the whole screen, and does not have the usual window decorations. "
"To exit full screen mode, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; "
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Spremeni &khelpcenter; v celozaslonski način, v katerem okno &khelpcenter; "
"zavzame celoten zaslon in nima običajnih okrasnih elementov. Za izhod iz "
"celozaslonskega načina pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; "
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Table of Contents</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>Dom</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kazalo vsebine</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgUp</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Page</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgUp</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnja stran</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous page of the current documentation."
msgstr "Pojdite na prejšnjo stran trenutne dokumentacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Page</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednja stran</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next page of the current documentation."
msgstr "Pojdite na naslednjo stran trenutne dokumentacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Left</keysym></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Levo</keysym></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go back to the previous page you were viewing."
msgstr "Vrnite se na prejšnjo stran, ki ste si jo ogledovali."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Right</keysym></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Desno</keysym></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have previously moved back with the back icon or menu entry, you can "
"work your way forward again with this menu entry."
msgstr ""
"Če ste se prej vrnili nazaj z ikono nazaj ali vnosom menija, se lahko s tem "
"vnosom menija ponovno pomaknete naprej."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Zaznamki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a bookmark for the current page, the title of the pages is appended to "
"the bookmarks menu. Use the action <guimenuitem>Delete Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem> in the context menu of an item to remove it from the menu."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte zaznamek za trenutno stran, naslov strani se doda v meni zaznamkov. "
"Z dejanjem <guimenuitem>Izbriši zavihek</guimenuitem> v kontekstnem meniju "
"elementa, ga odstranite iz menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
