"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguracija pisav...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to configure the font family and size used by &khelpcenter;."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča nastavitev družine in velikosti pisave, ki jo uporablja "
"&khelpcenter;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &khelpcenter; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega ima &khelpcenter; skupna menija &kde; <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite poglavja o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Menij "
"Nastavitve</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">Menij Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

